				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It seems I have to clarify something....
<br />

<br />
While it is true in normal RvR you lose no xp and no con for dying.  In the above situation I DID lose both.  Why?  Since I was in melee with a monster, the server thought I died due to PvE death.
<br />

<br />
As for the comment of staying away from frontiers...
<br />

<br />
There are times that quests will take you outside the realm.  Maybe you just want a change of pace from the usual critters in your realm.  Point is, if they not RvRing LEAVE them be!  If I wanted mindless killing of players I would play Quake or UT.  I could understand if I was high 40's and they thought I was a threat, but a grey has virutally no chance of harming you.  Not to mention when there is 1 grey and about 30+ of them.
<br />

<br />
Another incident happened again today.  I was in Darkness Falls in albion with my 31 paladin.  Not that far in really, just helping some low 20's guildies get some cash and xp.  Guess what?  Once again inconsiderate Hibernians slaugherted us.  Didn't even wait til we finished fighting the lilispawns that we were CURRENTLY fighting.  So all 3 of us lost xp as if we died due to normal PvE.  Again, the celt target was purple, as I'm sure most of the rest of the hibs were.  Did they feel good knowing they can kill grey players?  
<br />

<br />
Geez, people GROW UP.  Since you're out of high school and can't bully people there you come to this game to do it?  Even in real war, they wouldn't slaughter innocents or those people not a threat.  For those that may comment "well then don't go to DF/Frontier", I say this:  If it was meant to be a Level 50 Exclusive Club, there wouldn't be lower level critters in there.  
<br />

<br />
Sorry I am a little ticked at the moment.  Not only did I lose a chunk of xp, but I have a guildie that was in tears over being splattered all over the wall.  Great way to introduce this young kid to RvR Hibbies, hope you feel proud of yourself.  There is a lvl 19 mid in their frontier better go kill them quick, cuz they such a threat to you....    <img src="images/smiles/icon_mad.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
