				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I don't care why you are in the fronteer.
<br />

<br />
Any one that can observe and report movement is a poitential target.
<br />

<br />
I don't care what character I have out there, when I see an enemy group roll by, I report it to my alliance.  Numbers , Location, direction, and Levels.   Information is a valuble tool, having it for your side and keeping it from your opponenet is important.
<br />

<br />
Part of the war is keeping the other side from the good cash and exp that flows from DF.  Thats half the point of taking keeps .. getting the best hunting spot for your side and takeing it away from the other side.  That includes sweeping the place clean after it has changed hands.
<br />

<br />
If you chose to go into RVR areas to level, understand the risks/rewards.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
